                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2005-05-23</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Pleask ask yourself before you read this book if Michael Crichton is a scientist or a fiction writer.  Fiction and Science are two very different things.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Audubon Weighs In</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      /
                      <span>10</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
